Sentencas: The present study proposes an efficient method for optimal model parameters estimation of the Solid Oxide Fuel Cell by considering its nonlinear dynamic behavior.
Titulo: An optimal model identification for solid oxide fuel cell based on extreme learning machines optimized by improved Red Fox Optimization algorithm

Sentencas: The approach is relied on using a novel optimal model of Extreme Learning Machines (ELM) network based on metaheuristics.
Titulo: An optimal model identification for solid oxide fuel cell based on extreme learning machines optimized by improved Red Fox Optimization algorithm

Sentencas: The main purpose is to minimize the Mean Squared Error (MSE) be-tween the empirical output voltage data and the output voltage of the model by the sug-gested optimized ELM network.
Titulo: An optimal model identification for solid oxide fuel cell based on extreme learning machines optimized by improved Red Fox Optimization algorithm

Sentencas: The proposed ELM network is optimized by an enhanced design of the Red Fox Optimizer (IRFO) Algorithm to provide optimal results.
Titulo: An optimal model identification for solid oxide fuel cell based on extreme learning machines optimized by improved Red Fox Optimization algorithm

Sentencas: The suggested ELM-IRFO method is then testified on a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell case study and its results are compared with the GWO-RHNN method from the literature and ELM-RFO method to show its effectiveness.
Titulo: An optimal model identification for solid oxide fuel cell based on extreme learning machines optimized by improved Red Fox Optimization algorithm

Sentencas: The final results showed that the proposed ELM-IRFO has the minimum value of the Mean Squared Error (MSE) against the other comparative methods.
